## 🎥 **Project Overview**

<div align="center">

C:\Btech project\environment\images\Recording 2025-06-18 074241.mp4

*Experience the future of environmental sustainability in India*

</div>

**Environment India** is a comprehensive digital platform dedicated to promoting environmental awareness, sustainable development, and green initiatives across India. This website serves as a hub for environmental education, policy insights, and actionable solutions for a sustainable future.

